Staff at DUT are forging ahead with their strike over wage negotiations today. Hundreds of staff staged a protest at the Steve Biko Campus this morning. Milton Estrice of NEHAWU addressed the staff as well as media who were invited by DUT management for a briefing update on the on the strike impasse.
